Email Bloopers

Using email for prospecting and customer acquisition is
more difficult than ever. With the volume of messages
increasing at an unprecedented rate, you've got stiff
competition for the reader's attention. What's the
solution? Debbie will tell you (after a bit of venting).

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3996.html




