Online Advertising: Bouncing Back

It has been a tough year so far. It wasn't long ago when
everyone knew a millionaire; now you know at least three
people who have been laid off. For many, exuberance has
given way to insecurity. But the industry is responding in
the right way -- with innovation, not retreat.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3995.html





