The Plot Thickens

Storytelling is a sophisticated art form, practiced by many
and mastered by few. But do today's masters have the skills
to tell the story when it becomes nonlinear and
interactive? Perhaps. Or it might take an entirely
different skill set. But that chapter has yet to be written.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3992.html




