Can Portals Resist the Dark Side?

Quicker, easier, more seductive is the Dark Side. But
resistance is not futile. If we want to explore the new
worlds of the Web, seek out new search results, to go not
only where paid placements take us, then the Force will be
with us. And we will live long and prosper.


http://clickz.com/article/cz.3994.html


